<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Zamanat — Financial Ecosystem Map</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #1A2340;
    --navy-light: #243058;
    --gold: #C9A84C;
    --gold-light: #E8C97A;
    --gold-pale: #F5EDD4;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --off-white: #F7F6F2;
    --gray: #8892A4;
    --light-gray: #E8EAF0;
    --teal: #0D9488;
    --rust: #B85042;
    --slate: #4A5568;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--navy);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    color: var(--white);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 0;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D1526 0%, #1A2340 50%, #243058 100%);
    padding: 48px 60px 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -80px; right: -80px;
    width: 300px; height: 300px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,168,76,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .header-label {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .header h1 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .header h1 span { color: var(--gold); }

  .header-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* ARCHITECTURE LAYERS */
  .layers-section {
    padding: 40px 60px;
    background: #111827;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .layers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .layer-card {
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .layer-card.zamanat {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A2340, #243058);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
  }

  .layer-card.zigchain {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D3340, #0D5C70);
    border: 1px solid rgba(13,148,136,0.4);
  }

  .layer-card.distribution {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D1F3D, #3D2952);
    border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.3);
  }

  .layer-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .zamanat .layer-tag { color: var(--gold); }
  .zigchain .layer-tag { color: #34D399; }
  .distribution .layer-tag { color: #A78BFA; }

  .layer-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .layer-card p {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .layer-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .pill {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .zamanat .pill { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.15); color: var(--gold-light); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2); }
  .zigchain .pill { background: rgba(13,148,136,0.15); color: #6EE7B7; border: 1px solid rgba(13,148,136,0.2); }
  .distribution .pill { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.15); color: #C4B5FD; border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2); }

  /* MAIN CONTENT */
  .main {
    padding: 40px 60px;
    background: var(--off-white);
  }

  /* ZONE HEADERS */
  .zone-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .zone-header:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

  .zone-badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .zone-badge.sme { background: var(--navy); color: var(--gold); }
  .zone-badge.institutional { background: #1A3A2A; color: #6EE7B7; }
  .zone-badge.individual { background: #2D1F3D; color: #C4B5FD; }

  .zone-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  .zone-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--slate);
    margin-left: auto;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* PRODUCT GRID */
  .products-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .products-grid.two-col { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .products-grid.four-col { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }

  .product-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 20px;
    border-left: 3px solid transparent;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    position: relative;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .product-card.sme-color { border-left-color: var(--gold); }
  .product-card.institutional-color { border-left-color: var(--teal); }
  .product-card.individual-color { border-left-color: #8B5CF6; }

  .product-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px; right: 16px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--light-gray);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .product-icon {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: block;
  }

  .product-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .product-card p {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--slate);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .product-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .tag.gold { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.12); color: #8B6914; }
  .tag.teal { background: rgba(13,148,136,0.1); color: #0D7A70; }
  .tag.purple { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); color: #6D28D9; }
  .tag.rust { background: rgba(184,80,66,0.1); color: #9B3A2A; }
  .tag.navy { background: rgba(26,35,64,0.08); color: var(--navy); }

  .instrument-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--light-gray);
  }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .zone-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--light-gray), transparent);
    margin: 8px 0 40px;
  }

  /* SUMMARY TABLE */
  .summary-section {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 40px 60px;
  }

  .summary-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .summary-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .summary-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .summary-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .summary-number {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .summary-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* FLOW DIAGRAM */
  .flow-section {
    background: #111827;
    padding: 40px 60px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .flow-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 40px 1fr 40px 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .flow-node {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  .flow-node.highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.15), rgba(201,168,76,0.05));
    border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
  }

  .flow-node h4 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .flow-node p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .flow-arrow {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .flow-node .flow-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .flow-tag.gold-tag { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.2); color: var(--gold); }
  .flow-tag.teal-tag { background: rgba(13,148,136,0.2); color: #34D399; }
  .flow-tag.purple-tag { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.2); color: #A78BFA; }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer {
    background: #0D1117;
    padding: 24px 60px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  }

  .footer-brand {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .footer-note {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .layers-grid, .products-grid, .products-grid.four-col { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .summary-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .flow-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .flow-arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); }
    .header, .layers-section, .main, .summary-section, .flow-section, .footer { padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="header">
  <div class="header-label">ZigChain / Zamanat Ecosystem</div>
  <h1>The <span>Omnichain</span> Financial<br>Operating System</h1>
  <div class="header-sub">Investment Banking · Asset Management · RWA Infrastructure · Settlement Layer · Distribution</div>
</div>

<!-- ARCHITECTURE LAYERS -->
<div class="layers-section">
  <div class="section-title">Three-Layer Architecture</div>
  <div class="layers-grid">

    <div class="layer-card zamanat">
      <div class="layer-tag">Layer 1 — Product</div>
      <h3>Zamanat</h3>
      <p>Investment banking & asset management arm. Structures, underwrites, and packages financial products from real-world assets into investable instruments.</p>
      <div class="layer-pills">
        <span class="pill">RWA Structuring</span>
        <span class="pill">Underwriting</span>
        <span class="pill">SPV Management</span>
        <span class="pill">Regulatory</span>
        <span class="pill">Merchant Acquisition</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="layer-card zigchain">
      <div class="layer-tag">Layer 2 — Infrastructure</div>
      <h3>ZigChain</h3>
      <p>The settlement, execution, and tokenization layer. Mints RWA tokens, executes smart contracts, routes cross-border payments, and manages the on-chain lifecycle of every asset.</p>
      <div class="layer-pills">
        <span class="pill">Token Factory</span>
        <span class="pill">USDT0 Settlement</span>
        <span class="pill">LayerZero Bridge</span>
        <span class="pill">WME Dashboard</span>
        <span class="pill">Smart Contracts</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="layer-card distribution">
      <div class="layer-tag">Layer 3 — Distribution</div>
      <h3>Lenders & Investors</h3>
      <p>The capital deployment layer. Institutional lenders, asset managers, Islamic banks, sovereign funds, and retail investors who fund the products Zamanat structures.</p>
      <div class="layer-pills">
        <span class="pill">Institutional Lenders</span>
        <span class="pill">Islamic Banks</span>
        <span class="pill">Asset Managers</span>
        <span class="pill">Nawa Finance</span>
        <span class="pill">Retail via WME</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- MAIN PRODUCT MAP -->
<div class="main">

  <!-- ZONE 1: SME -->
  <div class="zone-header">
    <div class="zone-badge sme">Zone 1 — SME</div>
    <div class="zone-title">Business Liquidity Products</div>
    <div class="zone-desc">Extracting cash from stuck assets</div>
  </div>

  <div class="products-grid">

    <div class="product-card sme-color">
      <span class="product-number">01</span>
      <span class="product-icon">📄</span>
      <h4>Receivables Financing</h4>
      <p>Tokenize 90-day invoices into ONFTs. Lenders fund them instantly in USDT0. Merchant gets cash today — not in 90 days.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag gold">Trade Finance</span>
        <span class="tag navy">Factoring</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: Tokenized Invoice (ONFT)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card sme-color">
      <span class="product-number">02</span>
      <span class="product-icon">📦</span>
      <h4>Inventory-Based Lending</h4>
      <p>Stock sitting in a warehouse becomes collateral. Auditor (SGS/Intertek) verifies. Gold buffer (XAUt0) protects lender. USDT0 loan issued against verified stock.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag gold">Asset-Based Lending</span>
        <span class="tag teal">Gold-Backed</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: Vault-Locked Collateral</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card sme-color">
      <span class="product-number">03</span>
      <span class="product-icon">🌐</span>
      <h4>Cross-Border Settlement</h4>
      <p>B2B payments across borders in seconds. Buyer pays in USDT0, settled instantly via LayerZero. Gas fees paid in stablecoin — no volatile tokens required.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag gold">Payments</span>
        <span class="tag navy">B2B</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: USDT0 on ZigChain</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card sme-color">
      <span class="product-number">04</span>
      <span class="product-icon">🏦</span>
      <h4>Corporate Treasury Management</h4>
      <p>CFO dashboard showing Cash, Gold (XAUt0), and Tokenized Invoices in one view. Automated FX routing for local expenses. Fiat entry/exit via regulated ramps.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag gold">Treasury</span>
        <span class="tag teal">FX Management</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: WME Corporate Dashboard</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card sme-color">
      <span class="product-number">05</span>
      <span class="product-icon">🔗</span>
      <h4>Deep-Tier Supply Chain Finance</h4>
      <p>The big exporter's credit line passes down to sub-suppliers automatically. When anchor buyer pays, ZigChain smart contract routes each supplier's portion directly to their wallet.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag gold">Supply Chain</span>
        <span class="tag navy">Smart Contract</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: Programmable Receivable Split</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card sme-color">
      <span class="product-number">06</span>
      <span class="product-icon">🎯</span>
      <h4>Loyalty-Backed Credit Lines</h4>
      <p>Unredeemed corporate loyalty points (Stars, Miles) are an accounting liability. Tokenize them into a Loyalty Pool — borrow USDT0 against what was previously dead weight.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag gold">Liability Flip</span>
        <span class="tag rust">Loyalty</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: Tokenized Loyalty Pool</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="zone-divider"></div>

  <!-- ZONE 2: INSTITUTIONAL -->
  <div class="zone-header">
    <div class="zone-badge institutional">Zone 2 — Institutional</div>
    <div class="zone-title">High Finance & Capital Markets Products</div>
    <div class="zone-desc">Unlocking frozen institutional assets</div>
  </div>

  <div class="products-grid">

    <div class="product-card institutional-color">
      <span class="product-number">07</span>
      <span class="product-icon">📊</span>
      <h4>Investment Portfolio Tokenization</h4>
      <p>Bonds, equities, and funds used as collateral instead of being sold. Tokenize via Hadron by Tether. Mint a USDT0 credit line against frozen portfolio assets.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag teal">Securities</span>
        <span class="tag navy">Collateral</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: Tokenized Bond / Equity</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card institutional-color">
      <span class="product-number">08</span>
      <span class="product-icon">🥇</span>
      <h4>Gold Reserve Tokenization</h4>
      <p>Banks and sovereign funds turn physical gold bars into XAUt0 — digital super-collateral. Real-time proof of reserves on ZigChain. Can back a new local stablecoin.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag teal">Sovereign</span>
        <span class="tag gold">Gold-Backed</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: XAUt0 on ZigChain Ledger</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card institutional-color">
      <span class="product-number">09</span>
      <span class="product-icon">🛡️</span>
      <h4>Lender Safety Net (Gold Hedge)</h4>
      <p>Lenders in high-inflation regions require 10% XAUt0 buffer. If borrower defaults, lender claims gold. Held in Wakala (Shariah-compliant) structure — attracts Islamic institutional capital.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag teal">Risk Hedge</span>
        <span class="tag navy">Islamic Finance</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: Wakala Gold Vault</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card institutional-color">
      <span class="product-number">10</span>
      <span class="product-icon">🏗️</span>
      <h4>Fractional Fund Tokenization</h4>
      <p>A $100M locked fund opens to thousands of investors in small pieces. Fund Manager mints Fund Tokens via Hadron. WME automates legal rules and distributes USDT0 dividends automatically.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag teal">Private Equity</span>
        <span class="tag navy">Fund Management</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: Fund Token (ERC-20)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card institutional-color">
      <span class="product-number">11</span>
      <span class="product-icon">💎</span>
      <h4>Real Estate Tokenization</h4>
      <p>Commercial and residential property fractionally tokenized. Rental yield distributed automatically via smart contract. Unlocks illiquid real estate into tradeable positions.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag teal">PropTech</span>
        <span class="tag navy">Fractional</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: Property Token + Yield NFT</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card institutional-color">
      <span class="product-number">12</span>
      <span class="product-icon">📋</span>
      <h4>Private Equity & Bond Liquidity</h4>
      <p>Traditional PE and bonds are locked for years. Tokenize via Zoniqx engine. Secondary market on Oroswap DEX gives investors an exit before 10-year lock-up ends.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag teal">Secondary Market</span>
        <span class="tag navy">Fixed Income</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: Tokenized PE / Bond Token</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="zone-divider"></div>

  <!-- ZONE 3: INDIVIDUAL -->
  <div class="zone-header">
    <div class="zone-badge individual">Zone 3 — Individual</div>
    <div class="zone-title">Retail Wealth & Access Products</div>
    <div class="zone-desc">Institutional-grade tools for everyone</div>
  </div>

  <div class="products-grid four-col">

    <div class="product-card individual-color">
      <span class="product-number">13</span>
      <span class="product-icon">📱</span>
      <h4>Equity & Commodity Trading</h4>
      <p>Trade TSLA, NVDA, gold, oil from phone using USDT0 earned in Zone 1. Zero friction. AI-powered routing for best execution via Oroswap.</p>
      <div class="product-tags">
        <span class="tag purple">Perpetuals</span>
        <span class="tag navy">DEX</span>
      </div>
      <div class="instrument-label">Instrument: Perpetual Contracts</div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-card individual-color">
      <span class="product-number">14</span>
